translate ru HomeAloneApartment_9e0c9997:
    # "Sarah unlocks the door and steps into the apartment."
    ""

translate ru HomeAloneApartment_eff9b4f7:
    # "It's quiet."
    ""

translate ru HomeAloneApartment_749ab823:
    # "Cold."
    ""

translate ru HomeAloneApartment_b9f42079:
    # "She's alone. Alone with her thoughts, and all the good and ill that means."
    ""

translate ru HomeAloneApartment_c033b063:
    # "Sarah drops her bag on the nearby couch."
    ""

translate ru HomeAloneApartment_b3109538:
    # "A small puff of dust rises up."
    ""

translate ru HomeAloneApartment_8a806bcc:
    # "A reminder of just how long this house had sat empty."
    ""

translate ru HomeAloneApartment_52069ede:
    # "Sarah sighs, and the sounds echo of the undecorated walls."
    ""

translate ru HomeAloneApartment_d9499ffc:
    # "When Xan had still been alive, he had done more than teach her magic. He had also shown her the edges of the world."
    ""

translate ru HomeAloneApartment_5ba9cf06:
    # "He had always told her that the magic itself was only a small part of their order."
    ""

translate ru HomeAloneApartment_c629f793:
    # "That the real work was done in the shadows."
    ""

translate ru HomeAloneApartment_10b37b87:
    # "But died before he could introduce her into the order properly, before he could tell her all of his secrets."
    ""

translate ru HomeAloneApartment_2e3092c4:
    # "In no small part, her own doing."
    ""

translate ru HomeAloneApartment_8755012a:
    # "Sarah shuddered at the sudden rush of guilt over her betrayal."
    ""

translate ru HomeAloneApartment_d6336d5a:
    # "At the time, it seemed so necessary."
    ""

translate ru HomeAloneApartment_0adc2306:
    # "She had worked so hard to break free, make her own path, only for him to threaten to take it all away again."
    ""

translate ru HomeAloneApartment_aea4a7f7:
    # "Still, she could not deny the soft voice that tormented her for her actions."
    ""

translate ru HomeAloneApartment_d3b20d05:
    # "He had been kind to her, when nobody else in the world would."
    ""

translate ru HomeAloneApartment_88803496:
    # "And how had she repaid him?"
    ""

